Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*就算知道世界是黑暗的*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*也要試著喜歡它*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*不要東躲西藏*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*獻出我的心*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*它就能有節奏地*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*永跳不止*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*生命如此短暫*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠  你唱的什么歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夢里的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-很好聽哦  -*為什么...*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特蕾西發了郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新沙發來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想象中更綠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是照片的緣故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠  你還好嗎  菠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還在跟著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下  抓牢車子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了 抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶菠走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話給錢寧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他他們找到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我來了  -她失去意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷到哪里了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要急救
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這能讓你舒服一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傷害她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她放下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她放下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別移動她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打急救電話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救護車來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以告訴救護員  你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(172,210)\bord0\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK}金斯蘭監獄  佐治亞州
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒  塔特  伙計  你的神父來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們總這么玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在里面沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒要求見神父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有相當長的暴力史  塔特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被捕是十四歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后還因為搶劫和傷人多次入獄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  你因兩起謀殺罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將在半小時內被處決
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你沒什么要懺悔的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無辜的  我是被陷害的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過貌似沒人相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒人相信過你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天行刑  卻沒有家人朋友來看你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你服刑這七年  也從未有人來過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持活下去的希望都是很難的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括想要記住曾經的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要懺悔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就最好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生存的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都在尋求寬恕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無人尋得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來幫你逃獄的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是割傷和挫傷對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  但她還沒恢復意識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要確保沒有內傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請停下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她的大腦圖嗎  出錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-大腦系統確實在運作  -再測一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐一下  馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是答應了  你有什么要求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來不僅是為了還你自由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要給你份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚一男一女死于車禍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是一個叫菠的小女孩的養父母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫特  小心信號聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不是場意外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想要綁架這個小女孩卻失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在在圣安妮醫院  我們得在別人之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是個綁匪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有要你綁架她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來請你救她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小女孩非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你還有4分54秒的時間逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你他媽在說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這很好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有考慮嗎  還是只是固執己見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可在給你一條出路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離牧師遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4分28秒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我憑什么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信那些所謂的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-夠了  -你以為我為什么在這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了嗎  -好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我一支腎上腺素  一支阿托品[含顛茄]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了嗎  -好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生  可以結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡時間  晚上11點58分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖行過死蔭的幽谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\an8}出自舊約圣經《詩篇》第二十三章\N通常是為死刑犯最后的禱詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不怕遭害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有五十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思  他們說只是打砸搶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們陷害了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不關我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關燈  關閉系統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手呢  把你手給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有腳鐐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  現在打他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-來  打我  -賤人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往左邊走  左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  我們得快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥斯奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽5
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  他往那邊跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他往那邊跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿平靜與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也"很高興"見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  住手  關了它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  我叫溫特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要飛幾個小時  飛機上聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這計劃如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒讓你們銬著他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有點過于"積極"了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開他的手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么選他  他是個殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么不選我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我們晚點再說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫菠對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是庫里安醫生  是這里的住院醫師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這烏龜很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫斯坦利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我媽媽送給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的親生媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我不記得她了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還需要做幾項檢查  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那場車禍很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此我很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們才做了我兩個星期的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們那么和藹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個房間的病人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個好醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救了絲尼格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是絲尼格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  你還照顧過他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你累了  菠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晚點再來看你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senga怎么樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我不認識叫絲尼格的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是斯古洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯古洛斯  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小女孩現在圣安妮醫院里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我明天就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫特會保護她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-彌爾頓·溫特嗎  -是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就想讓大家這么認為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說得很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚不工作  今天是我媽媽生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是在圣安妮醫院的八樓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到她后聯系我  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,220)\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs18\b1}我很榮幸將今年的人道主義獎頒給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,240)\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs18\b1}羅曼·斯古洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打菠出生  就一直有神秘現象發生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些現象無法預測
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是和她的情緒有關
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在她還控制不了那力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會長大成才的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個被冤入獄的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能掰彎勺子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特先生  這是很非常真實的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冤入獄的那位也是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還可以掰彎小刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想在適當的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她為世界所用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有權勢的人會試圖綁架她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想把她全部天賦都據為己用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們覺得控制了她的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就控制了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么選我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最新科技  全球定位追蹤裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能確切地知道你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是為了保證你做完任務會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想脫下它  只能砍掉自己的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我會咬掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五分鐘后降落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會給我配槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特先生  你和好人共事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不上槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎  你辭職了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是因為這件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為你感到遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}祝爺爺早日康復
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該在重癥監護病房
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過急診室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她回來  然后跟桑托斯會合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他躺下吧  開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動  現在正好有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從梯子上跌落  受力兩臂有挫傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還算穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還算好  還有情況更糟的  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉  -不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下  里面那個女孩去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況穩定了  轉移到了普通病房
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我摔進了下水道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他們給我洗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:16:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我撞到頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉上的傷是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  你根本不覺得疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能摸一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我很疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的新養父嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  你太臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會跟你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就得跟我走  溫特說了你必須跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌爾頓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是溫特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫彌爾頓·溫特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你為什么哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說過了  傷很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是因為你想起來了你是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我們快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她去拍個片子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  我跟你們一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感覺怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  我會帶你過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院規定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我帶她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會害我丟了工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蘭醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉色有些發白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想良心不安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子別這么調皮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趴下  別開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩停車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會平安無事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-誰  -追我們的那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在她屁股上狠狠扎了一針
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會沒事的  我才不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們這是去哪  -我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-彌爾頓在哪  -我說了不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能安靜一會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}城市理發店
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道絲尼格是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲尼格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是普通病人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得告訴特里醫生  這樣他就不會辭職了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你女兒下車了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是我女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我自己也有安排  -很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他吃飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡力了  可他沒吃多少
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以周日再付我錢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  卡門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個今天病人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:22:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想救他  但沒成功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  以前也看過人死  但
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人  我真的很想救他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.67,0:23:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得你以前總跟我說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說就算我是地球上最后一個醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不會來找我看病
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永遠是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是那么強壯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么多想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你生病后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總想著要治好你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是  總是想讓你恢復健康
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓你知道你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.27,0:23:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你會感謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.18,0:24:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道我今天辭職了  你會很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.96,0:24:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是要爭到最后做贏的那一個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你卻沒法再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.84,0:24:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.12,0:24:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找地址
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能像那樣直接跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.15,0:24:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去奧斯維奧街14-22號
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.54,0:24:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡言亂語些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.56,0:24:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得告訴特里醫生關于絲尼格的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.24,0:24:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小屁孩能閉嘴聽我講話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.59,0:24:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那21任養父母也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.99,0:24:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.82,0:24:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你很傻  英語說得也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.93,0:24:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆  快進來  我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-錢寧  -我們得趕快走  快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.34,0:24:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.46,0:25:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.32,0:25:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該回救護車上的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.46,0:25:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.41,0:25:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個家伙把我打了個半死
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.43,0:25:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是家伙  是個女的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.95,0:25:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我就是說  -一個女的把你打了個半死
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.81,0:25:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.47,0:25:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個女的  長得很高大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.78,0:25:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一點都不高大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.81,0:25:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.18,0:25:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌爾頓
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.54,0:25:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來讓我抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.93,0:25:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又重了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.89,0:25:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有  我兩周之前才和你見過
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.46,0:25:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢寧  帶菠去看看新衣服  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.27,0:25:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些很漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.26,0:25:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.39,0:25:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-塔特先生  -我的腳環
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.14,0:25:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把它拿掉  -沒那么簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.26,0:25:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有過協定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.51,0:25:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是你為我工作
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.81,0:25:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作我已經做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.98,0:26:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作才剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.52,0:26:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你已經注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.39,0:26:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠是個非常特殊的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.11,0:26:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作是保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.46,0:26:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確保她的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.93,0:26:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓那個女人傷害她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.31,0:26:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人  以及她所效力的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.07,0:26:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會成為我的新養父嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.15,0:26:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等  寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.77,0:26:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很兇  而且身上很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.78,0:26:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掉到下水道里了  我都告訴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.45,0:26:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  她也不想和我待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.05,0:26:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.37,0:26:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最重要的責任  例如她的健康
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.70,0:26:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及她的教育  那是你的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.60,0:26:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫特  我想和你待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.68,0:26:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來寶貝  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.73,0:26:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.58,0:26:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經談過了  還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.24,0:26:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我接受的話  這工作需要幾個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.49,0:26:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.69,0:26:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要幾個月嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.80,0:26:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會是你一生中最精彩的幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.40,0:27:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們用了五年時間才找到線索
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.92,0:27:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你只用了一天就跟丟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.49,0:27:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夠了  蠢貨  發現什么了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.34,0:27:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾的摩地區僅有的相關資料是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.16,0:27:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫特在死前一年購買的房產
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.03,0:27:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地址是新柯克街
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.55,0:27:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16-105號  看上去像個倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.74,0:27:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在把坐標發到你的GPS上
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.26,0:27:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  轉一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.36,0:27:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.43,0:27:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-謝謝  -你喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.63,0:27:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方的本事大得很
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.51,0:27:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量避免使用電話和其他電子設備
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.45,0:27:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢寧會監控你的行蹤和進展
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.13,0:27:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我還沒同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.12,0:27:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當然同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.82,0:27:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿世界都在通緝你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.41,0:27:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯調局  警察  所有人都在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.71,0:27:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我可以碰碰運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.16,0:27:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出去之后十分鐘都堅持不了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.53,0:27:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一看到你就會射殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.31,0:28:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有了我們的幫助  你就不用擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.84,0:28:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是超級英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.01,0:28:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們是勤奮努力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.95,0:28:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.60,0:28:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒有回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.66,0:28:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么選我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.77,0:28:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.06,0:28:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你好好照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.32,0:28:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教育她  給她吃有機食品
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.93,0:28:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她住舒服的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.59,0:28:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從現在開始要撫養她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.13,0:28:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要一把槍
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.38,0:28:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.14,0:28:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.78,0:28:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你第一次看到她時就有所感覺  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.42,0:28:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.35,0:28:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感覺到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.10,0:28:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.75,0:29:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.60,0:29:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.33,0:29:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上菠
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.00,0:29:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎么找到我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.89,0:29:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問要去哪一層
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.87,0:29:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.95,0:29:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-斯坦利  -別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.90,0:29:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-別撿了  快走  -不  斯坦利
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.30,0:29:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快點  -快走
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.81,0:29:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不  -塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.74,0:29:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不  -塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.79,0:29:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.40,0:30:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.68,0:30:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦利
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.18,0:31:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科里  他們之前在這里  現在走了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.97,0:31:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還能去什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.19,0:31:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查查別的房子  別的人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.64,0:31:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.77,0:31:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再查查
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.67,0:31:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.04,0:31:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.14,0:31:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊  拇指姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.09,0:31:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開她
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.33,0:31:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫特
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.65,0:31:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你不打女人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.88,0:31:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在打了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.73,0:31:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.50,0:31:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.19,0:31:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.37,0:31:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.98,0:32:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.19,0:32:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.72,0:32:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.59,0:33:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.01,0:33:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.23,0:33:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-錢怎么辦  -別管錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.59,0:33:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.18,0:33:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.57,0:33:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.62,0:33:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了  沒事了  寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.66,0:33:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是鬧鬼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.69,0:33:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點嚇人  不過沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.43,0:33:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-溫特  -再快點  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.02,0:34:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.15,0:34:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所有的據點都不安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.93,0:34:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們得不斷轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.89,0:34:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會拖住她
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.82,0:34:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們現在就得下車
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.94,0:34:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.45,0:34:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠知道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.38,0:34:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下車
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.90,0:34:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別相信任何人  我們會去找你們
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.47,0:34:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌爾頓
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.15,0:34:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  帶上錢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.24,0:34:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上錢  躲那兒去  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.86,0:34:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14-20
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.10,0:34:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,120美元要過三年
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.85,0:34:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.93,0:34:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.35,0:34:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.91,0:34:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那事兒  你怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.01,0:34:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.22,0:34:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是剛才那群鳥  很詭異  到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.96,0:34:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那經常發生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.07,0:34:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想提那事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.02,0:35:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里還有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.81,0:35:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說餅干嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.13,0:35:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.96,0:35:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-特里  -不行  咱們走
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.91,0:35:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠  你在這干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.75,0:35:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要跟你說絲尼格的事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.45,0:35:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友需要幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.45,0:35:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.55,0:35:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個壞女人開槍打了他
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.63,0:35:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你受了槍傷  -不算什么  我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.17,0:35:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.77,0:35:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個非常出色的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.37,0:35:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你中了槍  我們必須報警
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.49,0:35:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能先幫我止一下血嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.42,0:35:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.11,0:35:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  進屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.73,0:35:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這沒有麻醉劑
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.98,0:35:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縫上就行
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.52,0:35:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  坐到桌子上
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.85,0:35:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掀起你的襯衫
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.27,0:35:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.54,0:35:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你父親
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.66,0:36:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不省人事了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.33,0:36:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時日不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.43,0:36:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很為你自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.29,0:36:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他不會
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.17,0:36:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.15,0:36:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲尼格怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.64,0:36:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過你我不知道那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.48,0:36:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我知道  -抗生素
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.88,0:36:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你認識絲尼格
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.00,0:36:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有時會弄錯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.21,0:36:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再深呼吸一次
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.36,0:36:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在還不認識她
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.69,0:36:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你會認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.54,0:36:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可能會有點疼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.65,0:36:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡量不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.69,0:36:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天她會病得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.16,0:36:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你能救她
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.16,0:36:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你她才能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.85,0:36:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.40,0:36:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲尼格是個歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.94,0:36:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  她非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.24,0:37:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們難過的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.68,0:37:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的音樂能讓他們開心起來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.75,0:37:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會治好她
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.33,0:37:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.26,0:37:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會治好很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.67,0:37:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你救治他這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.90,0:37:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再縫一針就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.02,0:37:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親認為你是個好醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.72,0:37:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道你努力想治好他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.32,0:37:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道他之前錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.52,0:37:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很抱歉從沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.29,0:37:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.78,0:37:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.83,0:38:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.63,0:38:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別沾水  盡量別搬東西
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.76,0:38:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要報警嗎  -算了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.96,0:38:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么知道這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.17,0:38:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  伙計
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.86,0:38:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是這么討人厭
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.55,0:38:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.61,0:38:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先進行胸外按壓  準備好手術室
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.41,0:38:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我十分鐘內趕到
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.54,0:38:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.78,0:38:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.49,0:38:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上運動衫  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.18,0:38:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡門  我是亞當
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.79,0:38:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道事出突然  但你得過來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.98,0:38:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被叫去醫院了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.87,0:38:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.38,0:39:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再見了  菠  -再見
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.73,0:39:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.46,0:39:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我們到底去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.45,0:39:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費城
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.17,0:39:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脾氣不好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.00,0:39:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你想跟我走  去另一個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.58,0:39:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得定幾條規矩  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.91,0:39:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.01,0:39:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.66,0:39:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個醫生不關你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.55,0:39:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多管閑事了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.38,0:39:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是他把你治好的  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.21,0:39:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.47,0:39:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到了別的地方  你少管別人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.91,0:39:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.45,0:39:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有姑娘掉進河里怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.58,0:39:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎  快向我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.41,0:39:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我看到有人在路上逆行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.29,0:39:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那天特別熱
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.46,0:39:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱到掉個硬幣
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.34,0:39:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能直接融化在路上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.50,0:39:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去撿硬幣手被黏住
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.73,0:39:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而一輛卡車正迎面而來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.68,0:39:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這根本不可能  -如果真的發生了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.03,0:40:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}來電  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.40,0:40:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她叫什么名字  -艾格尼絲
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.51,0:40:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾格尼絲
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.66,0:40:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫特  手背怎么樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.44,0:40:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又被保護起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.02,0:40:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.79,0:40:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被塔特保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.19,0:40:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得說這有點出人意料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.57,0:40:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這事早晚會出岔子的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.03,0:40:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯古洛斯越逼越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.88,0:40:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不敢相信咱們以前居然和那種人一伙
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.70,0:40:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過往總是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.51,0:40:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很神奇的  親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.46,0:40:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得不斷地讓他們在各城市間轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.02,0:40:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那太冒險了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.45,0:41:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們向好處看
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.45,0:41:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想那些她一路上能夠幫助到的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.88,0:41:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你找了個死刑犯當她同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.12,0:41:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.92,0:41:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她父親
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.87,0:41:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有月亮的碎片砸到了一間房子里
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.31,0:41:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里他們把蜘蛛關在籠子里  籠子壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.81,0:41:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后尼桑姆那里有個種田人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.07,0:41:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對蜘蛛過敏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.59,0:41:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這句話槽點太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.39,0:41:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二規矩是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.82,0:41:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一切照我說的做  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.07,0:41:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果我們正呆在冰屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.96,0:41:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你患上了寒冷腫瘤什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.05,0:41:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你叫我點蠟燭  可我聞到了瓦斯味
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.74,0:41:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  一定要點蠟燭
